{
  "texts": [
    "Below, we describe the authoring personas that we encountered.",
    "We then describe shared and distinctive patterns in the tasks they perform, the tools they use, and the general processes they take.",
    "Insights Users and ContextBased on the interviews, we found that genomics experts exhibit diverse types of visualization authoring processes and tool usage.",
    "The criteria mentioned, such as expressiveness or efficiency, also exhibit variations across different groups of users.",
    "Recognizing this diversity, we identified five personas that describe distinct groups of genomics data visualization authors: \"Biologists\", \"Computational Biologists\", \"Bioinformaticians\", \"Software Engineers\", and \"Visualization Experts\"."
  ]
}